{"tid":2155946,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岳義士生日快樂","createTime":"2020-08-14T06:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T07:06:58.000Z","uid":359790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4349bb15fe1cc8f5e22ddb79c1c77f722e709c","tid":2155946,"uid":359790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vt8GNUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVt8GNUF.jpg&h=4a289637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝岳義士陳以晉生日快樂   好人必有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac923dbf215355e85eb33b31ff66dd271c191e20","tid":2155946,"uid":21123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec21e2d49459d5cb5e4b68625aa489adb041830","tid":2155946,"uid":359790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"【獄中渡生日】<br />\n<br />\n大家生日的時候，都希望有人會對自己講句生日快樂，身陷港共黑獄的義士也不例外。<br />\n<br />\n去年9月15日遊行後，被稱為「岳義士」的陳以晉，在北角懷疑協助示威者逃離被捕，他襲警、管有攻擊性武器罪和拒捕罪成，在6月底被判囚十個月，現正在青少年監獄服刑。<br />\n<br />\n岳義士喜歡看歷史、地理、行山、露營的書，又會看港產片等等。他正式入獄前曾經講過，倉內有很多古惑仔，而且手足一個一個調倉或離開，令他感到孤獨，無人明白自己。<br />\n<br />\n下周就是岳義士的生日。一個活躍開朗的年輕人，突然要無辜面對失去自由和孤單的日子，實在一點也不容易，而他亦曾經講過，同道們每一句支持的話語，都是他在牢內的動力。<br />\n<br />\n本平台現呼籲同道們向岳義士送上生日卡，希望他知道很多同道都沒有忘記他，正等候他盡快重獲自由。<br />\n<br />\n同道可將生日卡寄到本平台：尖沙咀郵箱98697號。我們會將大家的心意，一一交到岳義士手中。<br />\n<br />\n只要每人多做一步，就可為身陷囹圄的義士送上無限溫暖；一句生日快樂，已可令在囚者感覺不被遺忘。義士們身陷港共黑獄的這段漫長苦日子，需要我們每一個人支持他們一起撐過去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521/2834480980172349/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1989972677956521%2F2834480980172349%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR08L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=fea2b349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521/2834480980172349/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"977a029c2bc39c1e93d484f2163230d48c69b9ae","tid":2155946,"uid":359790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73ac3f56621102d41bacc91df15bbcfaf36e969","tid":2155946,"uid":64636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:06:58.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<br />\n光<br />\n時"}]}